content.rendered:
For Cloteal Haynes, the partnership with Alticor Inc has created a path to success for her company HEW, based in Austin, Texas. Beginning as a small, local subcontractor, Haynes leveraged a mentor-protégé relationship to grow her business into a general contractor and respected partner firm in the community.

“Alticor Inc has helped me grow my business,” commented Cloteal Haynes, owner of HEW. “Our success is due to our true mutual partnership; this is much more than a transactional relationship.”

Alticor Inc succeeds by supporting the growth and success of trade partners like Haynes. Through a variety of targeted programs, Alticor Inc helps small businesses overcome challenges and roadblocks to achieve their goals and ambitions.
